snippet.description:
#JohnnyDepp #Virginia #AmberHeard
A REQUESTED UPDATE TO A VIDEO PERTAINING TO THE #VIRGINIA #CASE
*FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES ONLY*
Hey everyone.  Today's video is one that was requested pertaining to Johnny and Amber's case that's pending in Virginia.  What may come to pass?  Who may succeed in winning their arguements??  Please know that I went into this, like always, with the upmost respect and in the hopes to try to ascertain information that may help in some way.  This is only an attempt to try to ascertain information about this case the best that I can.  Thank you for your time and I hope this resonates for you!

Hello and welcome to my channel!  I’m Beauty Heathen and this is where we explore Paganism through the medium of cosmetics!  Not gunna lie, I’m more than a bit nervous doing this, but I felt it was time to end the misinformation and help inform and educate anyone who may be interested in this subject!  There will be beginner instruction on rituals and spellwork on this channel. For more advanced or adult themed instruction, be sure to follow my social media below and stay tuned for updates regarding my upcoming Patreon!  If you have any requests for a subject you may be interested in, please be sure to comment below and I will try to cover it in a future video!  With all of this said, welcome and let’s have fun learning together 😊

*Disclaimer*
No two pagans are alike and it will not always be feasible to verify information with practitioners of certain paths. I will do my best to cover information as well as I can. If anything is ever incorrect, please feel free to leave corrected/alternate information below. Respect is paramount on my channel. I have my own views and beliefs and respect those of others, but please remember that if yours differ, they are yours and please be respectful that mine are my own. If there is hate or derogatory comments, they will be deleted and users banned.
